fields.title: No Work Bread
fields.directions: 1. Combine ingredients, briefly 2. Cover and let sit 18+ hours at room temperature 3. Fold over two or three times 4. Preheat oven to 450°, including covered baking vessel 5. Turn dough into vessel and bake 30 minutes covered, 25 minutes uncovered

fields.title: Ants on a log
fields.description: This is a fun snack that kids can make.
fields.directions: Cut the celery stalks in half. Spread with peanut butter. Sprinkle with raisins.
